UdRhkTTMibGDvWbat9Mp9CFk1P9wfvUp4TavM8l2-jKovPIZZVCv1c9Q5bJYoRU7n37B2-J_B63=
sBeHuFldXVteoCHWL6AnTQWgxk97RjHXtLLk2KiYIxRPoq2KNtQuvx_0X-q2b03] that =E2=
=80=9Cto become the absolute best place to work, communication and collabor=
ation will be important, so we need to be working side-by-side. That is why=
 it is critical that we are all present in our offices.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
The simple inertia of doing things the way we=E2=80=99ve always been done.=
=C2=A0
Until now, they=E2=80=99ve been winning. Remote work grew at only an 8% CAG=
R between 2005-2014 based on data from the American Community Survey [https=
://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkU2OhCAQhU_T7MbwI3a7YDGbuYYBqVbSCIYCjXP6QV1=
MUnlFXqV45GPUGaaYDrVGzOSUIR8rqAA7esgZEikIaXBWsY6_hGx7YlVr2Uu-iMPhnQAW7bzKqQ=
BZi_Fu1NnFcG1QyiWZleyk7jWzhpm3sWwUVvdPqgXvJRf6Ke9cXayDMIKCDdIRAxCv5pxXfIjvB=
_-pte97M0LAgs0Ut2qsKU5JL_iFJW1wYLXQnZoAY0kjnOfNYdHe_V7POo05LmA0gv3aY_pAwmbO=
iydOccoZZUwwITvRN6zxs_2wUK8Sj5YuE2-wGMx6_DRjXEhSIWYTkwtTHX9mvYC_BhXDUPtSgsv=
HAEEbD_YmlG_QF7NhggCpfoAddK54GZVtx_q-lfQmUhEKxhjlvSA12ca6Ff5D_wA2UJog] admi=
nistered by the Census Bureau.
Having worked in the space for a while, Dan knows that the office isn=E2=80=
=99t going to go down without a fight, so he=E2=80=99s issuing a call-to-ac=
tion:=C2=A0
If you care about living in a world in which the air is cleaner, cities are=
 livelier, families are closer, women and minorities are enabled, and peopl=
e are happier, then the next time a traditional corporation, worker, or com=
mercial real estate bagholder tells you that real magic only happens inside=
 the office, take a stand.
There is a movement forming. Tens of millions of people have experienced th=
e benefits of remote work first-hand. Now, inertia is on remote=E2=80=99s s=
ide. Teamflow and other remote-first software and tools are going to make a=
n until-now hacked-together experience purposeful and delightful.=C2=A0
But the war is not won, and remote is not inevitable. Any good movement nee=
ds the best, brightest, and hungriest to lead. Via Teamflow, remote work ha=
s Flo Crivello.
